com.opengamma.strata.pricer.capfloor

Class NormalIborCapletFloorletExpiryStrikeVolatilities

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.pricer.capfloor.NormalIborCapletFloorletExpiryStrikeVolatilities
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MarketDataView, IborCapletFloorletVolatilities, NormalIborCapletFloorletVolatilities, Serializable, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class NormalIborCapletFloorletExpiryStrikeVolatilities
extends Object
implements NormalIborCapletFloorletVolatilities, ImmutableBean, Serializable
    Volatility for Ibor caplet/floorlet in the normal or Bachelier model based on a surface.

    The volatility is represented by a surface on the expiry and strike dimensions.
